1. **Analyze and Describe the Main Target Image:**

The main image shows a structure composed of 7 blocks.  There are three layers.  The blocks are arranged with some in a stacked configuration.  Spatial relationships include blocks sitting atop other blocks, some blocks positioned side-by-side, and a block with a notch that fits into a portion of a second block.

| Orange cylinder                          | 7           |
| Red block (small rectangular, horizontal)| 4           |
| Red block (small rectangular, horizontal)| 11           |
